title: Ebro In The Morning - Nets Basketball + Toe Talk
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/15.  

Ebro tells us who played themselves (16:00), and Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (12:30, 33:00 & 1:02:00). The Crew opens up the Toe Talk Line (38:00) and give some Guru-like advice (52:00).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
